title: Arianna Sanna
text: Arianna Sanna (born 8 May 1998) is a Dominican Republic <a href="Swimming%20%28sport%29">swimmer</a>. She competed in the <a href="Swimming%20at%20the%202017%20World%20Aquatics%20Championships%20%E2%80%93%20Women%27s%20200%20metre%20freestyle">women's 200 metre freestyle</a> event at the <a href="2017%20World%20Aquatics%20Championships">2017 World Aquatics Championships</a>.
